ers-adab","tag-paradise-jannah","tag-rulers","tag-warning-al-nudhr"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-8jP","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":39838,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/21\/shahadah-necessitates-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":31981,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Shahadah: Testimony of faith necessitates Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 21, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Suhayl ibn Bayda\u2019 reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, whoever testifies there is no God but Allah, then Allah will forbid him from entering Hellfire and require him to enter Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 199 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32319,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/19\/three-sinful-people-no-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":31981,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Arrogance: Three sinful people will not enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Salman reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThree people will not enter Paradise: an elderly person who commits adultery, a dishonest leader, and a conceited dependent.\u201d Source: Musnad al-Bazza\u0304r 2235 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652